summary: sometimes I feel uncomfortable to living as women. but it doesn’t mean I feel tired to being women. it’s not about gender role....
caption:
sometimes I feel uncomfortable to living as women. but it doesn’t mean I feel tired to being women. it’s not about gender role. i have to care about a survival in concrete jungle, and at the same time I have to care about myself.
(to be specific, my uterus, menstruation and many other things.) so, I would to say “fuck off I’m mess and there’s no problem, don’t make things to complicate.“

I also like to think that this painting is Krolock’s most treasured possession.
